items.text: The **2010 Movistar Open** was a [[LINK|lang_en|Tennis|tennis]] tournament played on [[LINK|lang_en|Tennis_court#Clay_courts|clay courts]]. It was the 16th edition of the [[LINK|lang_en|Chile_Open_(tennis)|Chile Open]], and was part of the [[LINK|lang_en|ATP_World_Tour_250_series|ATP World Tour 250 series]] of the [[LINK|lang_en|2010_ATP_World_Tour|2010 ATP World Tour]]. It took place in [[LINK|lang_en|Chicureo|Chicureo]] at the [[LINK|lang_en|Santiago_Metropolitan_Region|Santiago]]'s commune of [[LINK|lang_en|Colina,_Chile|Colina]][[CITE|1|http://www.adnradio.cl/noticias/deportes/torneo-movistar-open-se-jugara-en-el-club-piedra-roja-de-chicureo/20090903/nota/872931.aspx]] from February 1 through February 7, 2010.
